&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'.AppleSystemUIFont'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Ubuntu'; font-size:11pt;&quot;&gt;Simulate neuron data for the ampullary receptor cells of weakly electric fish for a population of neurons.  Use a table of model parameters and obtain simulated spike times for baseline activity and stimulation with a white noise stimulus.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Ubuntu'; font-size:11pt;&quot;&gt;(See &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;../../stimuli&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Ubuntu'; font-size:11pt; text-decoration: underline; color:#007acc;&quot;&gt;stimuli&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Ubuntu'; font-size:11pt;&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-family:'Ubuntu'; font-size:11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Ubuntu'; font-size:11pt;&quot;&gt;The input table must be a csv file, the model parameter in the same order as in the single simulation version. For example see&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
